Slurm
```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "description": "The script utilizes the Slurm workload manager for resource allocation and job execution.",
  "resources": {
    "nodes": 1,
    "tasks_per_node": 8,
    "gpu": 1,
    "partition": "gpu",
    "output_file": "output/slurm-%x.out",
    "error_file": "output/slurm-%x.err"
  },
  "environment": {
    "conda_environment": "cuda9-py38-pytorch1.5",
    "python_script": "supervised.py",
    "python_script_arguments": {
      "src_lang": "$SRC_LANG",
      "tgt_lang": "$TGT_LANG",
      "src_emb": "$SRC_EMB",
      "tgt_emb": "$TGT_EMB",
      "n_refinement": "0 or 5 depending on job type",
      "dico_train": "$DICO_TRAIN",
      "seed": "$SEED",
      "export": "pth",
      "exp_id": "${NAME}",
      "exp_path": "${EXP_PATH}",
      "dico_eval": "combined"
    }
  },
  "other_requirements": {
    "python_packages": ["supervised.py", "evaluate.py"],
    "script_arguments": [
      "SRC_LANG",
      "TGT_LANG",
      "SRC_EMB",
      "TGT_EMB",
      "NUM_LAYERS",
      "JOB_TYPE",
      "SEED",
      "ITERATE",
      "VOCAB_SIZE",
      "DICO_TRAIN"
    ]
  }
}
```
